<doc id="979320" wikidata="Q5564064" url="?curid=979320" title="Gippsland Grammar School">
<text>Gippsland Grammar School is a private Anglican co-educational boarding and day school. Located in Gippsland, Victoria. The School has three campuses, two in Sale, and one in Bairnsdale

Gippsland Grammar&#x27;s motto is &quot;Veritas Liberabit Vos&quot;, Latin for &quot;the truth will set you free&quot;.

